node.text: Happy 40th Birthday to the one and only, the Swiss Maestro, Roger Federer. Personification of elegance, class, professionalism hard work, respect & pure excellency. In the very top out of all athletes in any sport, very few things are as easy on the eye as that sweet one-handed backhand. Privilege to still see you play Roger. 🏆

node.text: Raging wildfires have erupted around the world in countries such as Italy, USA, Turkey, Spain, France, Cyprus, Finland, Lebanon, Canada & Greece just to name a few. There’s also been detrimental flooding in Italy, Belgium, Netherlands, Germany & China. Hail bigger than avocados have hauled down in northern Italy causing large damage. The second largest river in South America, Paraná River, is currently suffering from a severe drought. There’s even been snow in Brazil and tornadoes in Czechia.
